PROBLEM:
=======


WOOD PROCESSING FACTORY 

MUKESH AMBANI


WOOD PROCESSING

3 STAGES: 

DRILLING
CUTTING
PAINTING


HE HAS ONE PAINPOINT

FACTORY PRODUCED LESS PROCESSING FINSISHED GOODS THAN EXPECTED.

HE IS LOOKING FOR THE SOLUTION?

ONE GUYS COMEUP WITH SOLUTION


SOLUTION:
=========
IF WE CAPTURE AVG TIME TO PROCESSING WOOD PER MACHINE WITH HELP OF THESE 2 DATA POINTS 
START TIME
END TIME 

BASED ON AVG TIME TO PROCESS WOOD PER MACHINE

FIGURE OUT MORE TIME TAKING MACHINE - IT REQUIRES EITHER MAINTAINENCE OR REPLACE WITH NEW MACHINE.
 







